<div class="container py-4">

    <div class="page-intro-header mb-4">
        <h2 class="fw-bold text-dark text-center mb-1">West Virginia DMV Forms</h2>
        <p class="text-secondary text-center mb-3">
            Access, download, and print official DMV applications and forms online.
        </p>
        <hr class="mt-0" />
    </div>

    <div class="row g-3 mb-4">
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="info-card h-100">
                <div class="info-card-icon">📋</div>
                <h6 class="fw-semibold text-dark mb-1">Available Forms</h6>
                <p class="text-secondary small mb-0">
                    West Virginia residents may view, print, and save applications and forms for
                    driver's licenses, vehicle titles, registrations, address changes, and other
                    DMV services. Forms are also available at any
                    <strong>DMV Regional Office</strong>.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="info-card h-100">
                <div class="info-card-icon">🔍</div>
                <h6 class="fw-semibold text-dark mb-1">Searching for a Form</h6>
                <p class="text-secondary small mb-0">
                    Use the search tool below to find forms by <strong>title</strong>,
                    <strong>form number</strong>, or <strong>category</strong>. If you cannot
                    locate a form, try a partial keyword. Filtering by category can help narrow
                    your results further.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="info-card h-100">
                <div class="info-card-icon">📥</div>
                <h6 class="fw-semibold text-dark mb-1">Viewing &amp; Printing</h6>
                <p class="text-secondary small mb-0">
                    Click any form title to open it in your browser. All forms are in
                    <strong>Adobe Acrobat PDF</strong> format. You may view, print, or save them
                    using the free
                    <a href="https://get.adobe.com/reader/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                        Adobe Acrobat Reader
                    </a>.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="notice-banner mb-4">
        <strong>&#9432; Note:</strong> A PDF viewer such as
        <a href="https://get.adobe.com/reader/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Adobe Acrobat Reader</a>
